    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《种子成长》，这是一款卡组策略游戏，在这里您可以体验将自己的种子培育成果树的激动人心的过程。使用一套实用卡牌来种植、剪切某些部分，甚至利用周围环境为自己谋利。但要做好应对突发情况的准备--天气多变，虫害猖獗，每天都有新的挑战需要克服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/3e54d5cc185c89691d67f072eef8c3c7.avif?t=1746483445\" width=615 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/bb57b23ed3fcb807129ba289c7af9892.poster.avif?t=1746483445\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/bb57b23ed3fcb807129ba289c7af9892.webm?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/bb57b23ed3fcb807129ba289c7af9892.mp4?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想象一下，在模拟游戏中从一粒种子长成一棵树。您可以让种子生根，寻找水源或其他养分；如果树根腐烂或没有足够的食物维持树的大小，您也可以将树根砍掉。您还可以种植和剪切树的其他部分，如茎、叶、花或果实。此外，你甚至还可以操控周围的环境，让树木茁壮生长。现在，所有这些操作都仅限于使用纸牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/55bc380f7f78422dbc422e68f6d13a8d.avif?t=1746483445\" width=615 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/37bc498149c7b8dc86b7985c5fd134ed.poster.avif?t=1746483445\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/37bc498149c7b8dc86b7985c5fd134ed.webm?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/37bc498149c7b8dc86b7985c5fd134ed.mp4?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗卡牌游戏中，您可以使用卡牌造成伤破坏、保护自己或执行其他操作。而在 “种子成长 ”游戏中，卡牌可以用来培育你的树。你可以向特定方向种植根或莖，长出树叶进行光合作用，或一朵花，希望它能结出果实。好吧，即使它失败了，开始枯萎，也不要着急--把它砍掉！没有更多的土壤或水可以为光合作用提供养分或水分了吗？别说了，再加点土吧！当然是用卡片。如果你还有足够的奇迹的话，当然也可以使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/ffb5d3f35c016c32e8f00c8d45c8bdd2.avif?t=1746483445\" width=615 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/1db0cf9535a4ec456fdcbb43935b3c0a.poster.avif?t=1746483445\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/1db0cf9535a4ec456fdcbb43935b3c0a.webm?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/1db0cf9535a4ec456fdcbb43935b3c0a.mp4?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有足够的食物并不是阻止你繁荣的唯一障碍。毛毛虫、乌鸦和其他害虫也会损害你的珍贵树木。不过不用担心，当它们来袭时，你可以点击它们把它们击退！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/41cd3661d6d81ce2cfad4290f4334765.avif?t=1746483445\" width=615 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/c93d313b194230c884a1adcef07aff51.poster.avif?t=1746483445\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/c93d313b194230c884a1adcef07aff51.webm?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/c93d313b194230c884a1adcef07aff51.mp4?t=1746483445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当您种完树并感到满意后，您可能会渴望继续种植更多的树。这就是挑战的由来！您可以选择不同的种子，选择不同的地形，每种地形都有自己的噱头和挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能把种子培育成一棵美丽的果树吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336690/extras/81220dec233851e6a6b16a7352cb00b0.avif?t=1746483445\" width=615 height=64 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制游戏增加了策略和规划的体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从简单的入门卡组开始，随着游戏的深入，您可以解锁更多的卡牌，探索众多卡牌来培育您的植物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过选择茎、根和叶的延伸位置，选择植物的生长方式。优化资源，提前规划分枝，甚至根据自己的喜好塑造植物形状。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护您的植物免受害虫入侵，但动作要快！快速点击，打败害虫，获得丰厚奖励。使用正确的工具造成更多破坏，保护植物不受伤害。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对不断变化的天气条件，它们既能阻碍也能帮助你的植物生长。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演不同的种子，每个种子都有自己独特的植物形状和启动牌，努力实现特定目标。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索不同的区域，迎接不同的挑战，获得不同的奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拍下您的美丽作品，与全世界分享，或将其加入您的个人收藏夹。</p></li></ul>",
